{"tid":493480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Sharp 想要組成「日本聯盟」，對抗獨大的 OLED 韓國對手","createTime":"2017-12-08T14:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T03:58:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc19b913e353193d4deb8d19f1aae128deb049ac","tid":493480,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"2017/12/08<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/c5c1a88023bb011dd8846444dc8cfea3/205932226/dims-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fc5c1a88023bb011dd8846444dc8cfea3%2F205932226%2Fdims-1.jpg&h=bcf61903&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重新回歸東京證券交易所第一部（也就是我們說的主板）的 Sharp，在昨天的記者會上，CEO 戴正吳表示希望能跟國內對手 Japan Display 合作組成「日本聯盟」，對抗目前顯示面板市場被韓國品牌獨大的現況。<br />\n年初時有指 Sharp 計劃推出 OLED 電視產品，但在報導之後的一個月，LG 就表示在未來三年投資 70 億美元至其 OLED 業務的發展上。這難免叫歷經風浪的 Sharp 感到壓力。戴正吳在記者會上提到，他們正向日本政府商討組成全日本聯盟，並有可能投資到 Japan Display 的子公司 JOLED 上。JOLED 最近有釋出量產「印刷式」OLED 面板產品的消息，成本會比韓國主流使用的蒸鍍方式更便宜。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於現在 OLED 面板不管是商用，甚至連消費級產品也有強勁的需求，不過現時市場上卻只有一至兩家主要生產商，要是這個「日本聯盟」能夠順利組成的話，必然會為 OLED 市場帶來競爭，促進發展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/12/08/sharp-japan-alliance-oled-competition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2Fsharp-japan-alliance-oled-competition%2F&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cfa1cd9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/12/08/sharp-japan-alliance-oled-competition/</a>"},{"pid":"54f844bc7b15f40d0bbea4871f3184ddde32f840","tid":493480,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"太遲"},{"pid":"fd06652be69a5a5f8953b0886788c10acba34a9c","tid":493480,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"日本仔太守舊錯失時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68a03b4283be2d34e1a2e078314eb